        "solution_text": "$3a \\times 12$\n$= (3 \\times 12)a$\n$= 36a$"
      },
      {
        "question_text": "Simplify $x \\times x$.",
        "solution_text": "$x \\times x$\n$= x^2$"
      },
      {
        "question_text": "Simplify $15x \\div 5$.",
        "solution_text": "$15x \\div 5$\n$= \\frac{15x}{5}$\n$= 3x$"
      },
      {
        "question_text": "Simplify $\\frac{4ab}{2a}$.",
        "solution_text": "$\\frac{4ab}{2a}$\n$= 2b$"
      }
    ],
